		<section id="about-us" class="section-padding">
			<div class="content-layout">
				<div class="content-text">
					<h3 class="section-title" style="text-align: left" data-i8n="about_us_title">Our Story</h3>
					<p data-i8n="about_us_desc1">Kozara Panoramic Resort was created out of love for nature and the idea that luxury and peace can exist in perfect harmony. Our mission is to create a place where every guest feels a deep balance between nature, comfort, and serenity. Nestled in the heart of Mount Kozara, the resort offers an unforgettable experience where every detail reflects warmth, care, and elegance.</p>
					<p data-i8n="about_us_desc2">Our modern chalets offer privacy and intimacy, while still providing all the amenities of contemporary accommodation. Panoramic views, pure mountain air, and forest silence make every morning special and every evening calm. Kozara Panoramic Resort is more than a place to stay ‚Äì it‚Äôs an experience that restores inner balance, reconnects you with nature, and reminds you how little is needed to feel true peace. Welcome to a space where time slows down and every moment becomes a lasting memory.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="content-image">
					<img src="assets/Text Blocks/image08198.webp" alt="Hiking sign" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="about-kozara" class="section-padding blog-section">
			<div class="content-layout reverse">
				<div class="content-text">
					<h3 class="section-title" style="text-align: left" data-i8n="about_kozara_title">Discover Kozara</h3>
					<p data-i8n="about_kozara_desc1">Mount Kozara, known as the ‚Äúair spa‚Äù and the green jewel of Krajina, is a place where nature still breathes freely. Its dense forests, pure air, and peaceful viewpoints offer the perfect escape from city life. Kozara blends wilderness and tranquility, creating an ideal setting for relaxation, adventure, and self-discovery. Mount Kozara, known as the air spa and green oasis of Western Krajina, is where nature reveals its true beauty. Its dense forests, mountain streams, and fresh air make it a perfect retreat for rest, adventure, and spiritual renewal. The mountain trails lead through scenic viewpoints and fragrant meadows, offering views that calm the soul and fill you with energy.</p>
					<p data-i8n="about_kozara_desc2">Kozara is more than a mountain ‚Äì it‚Äôs an experience of connection with nature, a place where time slows down and thoughts become clear. Every visitor finds their moment of peace here, whether in the quiet of the forest, the whisper of the wind, or the sunset that paints the peaks in golden tones. Kozara invites you to pause, breathe deeply, and feel what true freedom means.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="content-image">
					<img src="assets/Text Blocks/Kozara-fotobaza-Ajdin-Kamber.webp" alt="Kozara amenity" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

