					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_kitchen_q" data-i8n="faq_kitchen_a" summary="What is included in the kitchen?"> The kitchens are fully equipped for self-catering. Features include a hob, large oven, microwave, large fridge-freezer, dishwasher, cookware, dishes, and glassware. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_linens_q" data-i8n="faq_linens_a" summary="Do I need to bring linens or towels?"> No. Bed linens and 100% cotton towels are provided. Bathrobes and swimming pool towels are available upon request. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_wifi_q" data-i8n="faq_wifi_a" summary="Is there internet access?"> Yes, Wi-Fi access is provided. The network name and password will be given to you at check-in. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_pool_heating_q" data-i8n="faq_pool_heating_a" summary="Are the pools private and heated?"> Yes, each chalet has its private pool (seasonal opening times). </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_lifeguard_q" data-i8n="faq_lifeguard_a" summary="Is there a lifeguard at the pool?"> No. Pool use is entirely at your own risk. Parents must supervise children at all times. Please note that only plastic glasses are allowed in the pool area. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_checkin_q" data-i8n="faq_checkin_a" summary="What are the check-in and check-out times?"> <b>Check-in:</b> 14:00 ‚Äì 22:00. <br /><b>Check-out:</b> By 09:00.<br />Note: Early check-in or late check-out may be possible depending on availability; please contact reception in advance. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_deposit_q" data-i8n="faq_deposit_a" summary="Is a security deposit required?"> Yes. A <b>‚Ç¨250 credit card</b> deposit is pre-authorized at check-in. This is a temporary hold to cover damages or unpaid extras and is released a few days after check-out if no issues are reported. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_cancel_q" data-i8n="faq_cancel_a" summary="What is the cancellation policy?"> <b>Standard Season (April‚ÄìJune, Mid-Sept‚ÄìOct):</b> 25% refund >14 days before arrival; 50% refund 7‚Äì13 days before. No refund if <7 days.<br /><b>Peak Season (July, August, Holidays):</b> No cancellations or refund available </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_payment_q" data-i8n="faq_payment_a" summary="What payment methods are accepted?"> We accept Visa, Mastercard, and American Express. Tourist tax is added to the booking. Extras can be paid by cash or card at check-out. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_tax_q" data-i8n="faq_tax_a" summary="Is there a tourist tax?"> Yes, a tourist tax is charged per person, per night. The rates are as follows:<br /><b>Adults:</b> ‚Ç¨1.30 per night.<br /><b>Children (12 to 18 years):</b> ‚Ç¨0.80 per night.<br /><b>Children (under 12 years):</b> Free of charge. </sl-details>
				</div>

				<div>
					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_shops_q" data-i8n="faq_shops_a" summary="Where are the nearest shops and restaurants?"> <b>Turjak (approx. 4 km):</b> Nearest grocery store, restaurants, and caf√©s.<br /><b>Gradi≈°ka (approx. 20 km):</b> Larger supermarkets, pharmacies, and main highway connections. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_housekeeping_q" data-i8n="faq_housekeeping_a" summary="Is housekeeping included?"> Could be provided for stays longer than 7 days. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_laundry_q" data-i8n="faq_laundry_a" summary="Do you offer laundry services?"> Upon request. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_baby_q" data-i8n="faq_baby_a" summary="Is equipment available for babies?"> No. We do not provide baby cots or highchairs, so we strongly advise parents to bring their own equipment for their children. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_pets_q" data-i8n="faq_pets_a" summary="Are pets allowed?"> Yes, pets are allowed upon request. Please note there is an additional fee of ‚Ç¨15 per stay. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_parking_q" data-i8n="faq_parking_a" summary="Is parking available?"> Yes, there is free private parking directly next to each chalet. </sl-details>

