					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_quiet_q" data-i8n="faq_quiet_a" summary="When are the quiet hours?"> Quiet hours are from 22:00 to 08:00. (Exceptions may be made if one group has booked all 5 chalets). </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_airport_q" data-i8n="faq_airport_a" summary="How far is the airport?"> Banja Luka airport is approximately 45 minutes by car. Transfers and local taxi services can be arranged upon request. </sl-details>

					<sl-details data-i8n-summary="faq_yearround_q" data-i8n="faq_yearround_a" summary="Is the resort open all year-round?"> Yes. </sl-details>

